00:00:16.860 --> 00:00:19.220
 Episode 02: Shinra Company 

00:00:22.420 --> 00:00:23.360
 Hey Rude, get along! 

00:00:23.880 --> 00:00:29.960
 [Reno Turks (Special Unit of Shinra, Inc.) WORLD VII] 

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:33.600
 Quiet, Reno. 

00:00:34.100 --> 00:00:40.000
 [Rude Turks Member (Special Unit of Shinra, Inc.) WORLD VII] 

00:00:40.900 --> 00:00:43.080
 Are you rusty, or what? Lets' go ! 

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:07.340
 Brrrrrrrrrrr I'm frozen! I have to dress more warmly! 

00:01:19.120 --> 00:01:20.300
 [Snowball attack] 

00:01:56.340 --> 00:01:57.020
 By the way, 

00:01:57.060 --> 00:02:00.000
 The hair regrowth of Professor Hojo is very effective. 

00:02:00.080 --> 00:02:01.920
 Thank you. Your scarf is very pretty, too. 

00:02:01.980 --> 00:02:03.280
 Lets' go. 

00:02:15.180 --> 00:02:17.200
 What? One again ? 

00:02:17.340 --> 00:02:20.400
 Did you kill my brother? 

00:02:20.540 --> 00:02:22.960
 Yeah, and it's your turn! 

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:26.400
 Then my brothers will avenge me! 

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:29.060
 But how much are you? 

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:33.380
 We are the siblings of the hundred snowmen of Mount Narshe! 

00:02:33.440 --> 00:02:36.100
 We do not have time for you all. See you ! 

00:02:57.200 --> 00:03:01.240
 The book that Rufus wants is kept by the Snow Clan. 

00:03:01.300 --> 00:03:03.100
 We have already seen the brothers of the family. 

00:03:03.200 --> 00:03:05.460
 The babysitter should not be far away. 

00:03:05.560 --> 00:03:09.700
 Who would have thought that the Forbidden Book of Elders would be here? 

00:03:09.780 --> 00:03:12.920
 I have a bad feeling. Let's finish! 

00:03:38.400 --> 00:03:42.480
 He will be safe here. 

00:03:47.760 --> 00:03:52.980
 We should attack before his mother comes back. Let's go get this book! 

00:03:54.220 --> 00:03:55.200
 Hold on ! 

00:03:56.140 --> 00:03:57.780
 I have an impression of déjà vu ... 

00:03:57.900 --> 00:04:00.300
 Let's take a look in the official guide. 

00:04:05.860 --> 00:04:07.120
 Hmm ... 

00:04:08.100 --> 00:04:08.780
 You are right ! 

00:04:08.880 --> 00:04:12.260
 They say to pay attention to the special attack "Frost". 

00:04:13.840 --> 00:04:16.720
 Fortunately I still have frost bracelets on me. 

00:04:21.140 --> 00:04:22.060
 What do you want ? 

00:04:22.340 --> 00:04:28.640
 [Princess Saphiria - Snow Clan - Mistress of Frost WORLD VII] 

00:04:32.840 --> 00:04:35.140
 The Forbidden Book of Elders! 

00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:38.800
 Do not touch it! It's far too dangerous! 

00:04:39.060 --> 00:04:42.360
 Do you want this world to be destroyed? 

00:04:43.080 --> 00:04:44.880
 If you refuse to give it to us of your own free will ... 

00:04:46.180 --> 00:04:47.800
 We will take it by force! 

00:05:26.640 --> 00:05:30.980
 Received: Key Element [Forbidden Book of Elders]! 

00:05:31.800 --> 00:05:35.840
 Received: [Shiva] Mistress of Ice Cream! 

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:38.420
 Forgive me, Mother! I failed. 

00:05:38.480 --> 00:05:41.040
 But I will not let them run away! 

00:05:41.480 --> 00:05:42.980
 It was easier than I thought. 

00:05:43.720 --> 00:05:45.580
 Wait a minute ... Do you hear that? 

00:05:55.860 --> 00:05:57.380
 An avalanche !!! 

00:06:04.560 --> 00:06:05.800
 He was less one. 

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:07.440
 No problem, we have the book! 

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:08.580
 We go back to Midgar! 

